00:00:00.260 --> 00:00:02.260
Today is Shri Datta Jayanti (centenary).

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:05.260
Today is a very great day.

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:10.660
I think this day has come only because of His blessings

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:14.040
that sahaja yoga has been blossomed in you people.

00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:21.260
The Guru of all the Gurus – Adiguru Shri Datta Maharaja.

00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:27.680
I bow to him, He is my Guru also.

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:33.000
He has taught me quite enough on Sahaja Yoga

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.540
all through my many births.

00:00:34.620 --> 00:00:38.240
And because of that only I have been able to do some work in this birth also,

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:40.140
continuing to do

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:44.540
Gurur Brahma Gurur Vishnu Gurur devo Maheshwara,

00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:49.760
Guru sakshat Parabrahma tasmai Guru dev namah.’

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:55.720
By the time Adyashakti created the universe

00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:00.240
after creating the entire universe

00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:04.000
like how a King spread out his kingdom

00:01:04.820 --> 00:01:09.100
and comes to see the world thereafter in a disguise

00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:14.000
in the same way Adishakti has also incarnated on this earth many a times.

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:19.100
But no matter how supreme is Adishakti

00:01:20.060 --> 00:01:22.220
she still needs a human Guru.

00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:25.260
The place of man is still superior to that power.

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.320
If Shakti has to take form of a human being

00:01:29.580 --> 00:01:31.580
then she is required to come on this earth

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.140
only after having achieved Her father sometimes

00:01:34.220 --> 00:01:37.560
Her brother sometimes and Her son sometimes.

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:44.100
First of all try to understand

00:01:44.620 --> 00:01:49.900
that entire universe was created by Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesha

00:01:51.980 --> 00:01:59.180
At that time a thought came in Adhishakti’s mind to lift people out of the world

00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:01.020
who were stuck in it,

00:02:01.340 --> 00:02:04.160
and that if these three principles

00:02:04.300 --> 00:02:07.180
were to be combined together somehow and the childlikeness

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:11.040
and innocence of Shri Ganesha could be absorbed by it

00:02:11.180 --> 00:02:15.940
then it is possible to form a Guru from them who has to do a great task.

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:19.240
She (Adishakti) was incarnated in the form of sati Anusuya.

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:23.460
This is the only such a sati (a chaste woman faithful to husband) in the whole world

00:02:23.720 --> 00:02:29.000
who has thought of emancipation of the human beings.

00:02:31.460 --> 00:02:33.460
This is a very great thing.

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:36.960
These three children came to Anusuya.

00:02:37.860 --> 00:02:40.480
The meaning of Anusuya is the one who is void of envy;

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.400
she does not envy anyone,

00:02:43.300 --> 00:02:45.300
who is the universal love

00:02:46.320 --> 00:02:48.280
In such a person there is no place for insignificant,

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:49.480
petty thoughts

00:02:50.100 --> 00:02:55.120
such as jealousy, anger etc.

00:02:56.820 --> 00:02:59.560
The one who does not have any asuya she is Anusuya.

00:03:00.460 --> 00:03:04.940
It is said that these three went to her door to examine her.

00:03:06.380 --> 00:03:08.880
And that moment she used her

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:10.620
tejbal (powerful radiance)

00:03:10.620 --> 00:03:12.140
– what was this tejbal;

00:03:12.420 --> 00:03:15.200
this was the love of mother, very much divine,

00:03:15.700 --> 00:03:17.700
love of a powerful mother.

00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:22.100
This tejbal fell on them

00:03:22.100 --> 00:03:23.800
and they became small children.

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:27.340
Their complete unified form is Shri Datta Maharaj.

00:03:27.340 --> 00:03:28.880
He is a strange majesty ,

00:03:29.100 --> 00:03:31.440
whatsoever description is made of him but will fall short.

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:34.680
And even if this is made to be explained, it will be beyond explanation.

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:38.200
This is Shri Datta Maharaj who is full of triguna (three attributes).

00:03:38.620 --> 00:03:41.380
He came in the world in form of Adiguru many times

00:03:41.460 --> 00:03:43.600
to teach how to cross the Bhavsagara (void).

00:03:43.900 --> 00:03:47.040
Yesterday I have told you that we fight in the world by forming many religions.

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:52.120
The same Shri Datta incarnated many a times on the earth.

00:03:53.020 --> 00:04:00.520
As I told you yesterday, King Janaka was one of them.

00:04:03.340 --> 00:04:08.360
King Janaka was the father of Janaki (Sitaji).

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:14.260
He was none other than the incarnation of Shri Dattatreya.

00:04:15.040 --> 00:04:20.120
Thereafter, Machindernath, most have you must have heard his name, was also His incarnation.

00:04:21.380 --> 00:04:25.940
After that Zoroaster who came three times on the earth,

00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:29.280
he was also His incarnation.

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:33.700
After that Mohammad Sahab,

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:41.080
who was His incarnation.

00:04:41.420 --> 00:04:45.820
And when he was asked that- ‘Bhai (Brother) there must have been others also before you?

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:48.440
Then he replied, ‘ yes, there a Mohammad’.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:51.860
Then again he was asked who was before him. He replied, ‘there was one Mohammad’

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:57.180
Mohammad means Praise, the one who is praised, the one who deserves to be praised

00:04:57.420 --> 00:05:01.400
and is the one who is redeemer of the world

00:05:01.620 --> 00:05:06.840
They were all Mohammads, they were all Dattatreyas,

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:10.580
who came on earth regularly.

00:05:12.020 --> 00:05:14.280
After that Nanaka, Guru Nanaka.

00:05:15.020 --> 00:05:16.880
If you ever read his teachings,

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:19.280
if you read his talks

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:23.620
then you will be surprised that he has always talked in a Sahaja.

00:05:23.860 --> 00:05:26.040
He has said “sahaja Samadhi lago”

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:33.360
He has said, ‘kahe re ban khojan jayi, sada niwasi sada alepa tohe sang samai,

00:05:33.540 --> 00:05:41.940
pushpa madhya jo was basat hai mukur mahi jas chhayee, taise hi hari base nirantar ghat hi khojo bhai’

00:05:41.940 --> 00:05:43.480
- why to go to forest to find Him,

00:05:43.540 --> 00:05:46.040
He is always there with you just like there is a fragrance in a flower

00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:48.100
and just as the reflection is there in a mirror,

00:05:48.100 --> 00:05:49.840
in the same way God is residing in you eternally seek Him within.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.720
He is just inside, achieve him just inside.

00:05:51.840 --> 00:05:53.340
We are just singing poem, singing songs, we are just cramming his prescription.

00:05:53.340 --> 00:05:55.940
The talk of seeking this absolute principle, residing just inside the heart, has been made since ancient times

00:05:55.940 --> 00:06:00.980
by these Adi Gurus, who are incarnated on this earth again and again.

00:06:01.980 --> 00:06:05.460
After the birth of the daughter of Mohammad Sahab,

00:06:05.640 --> 00:06:10.220
as I talked yesterday also, there was beginning of the caste “Shia” in Islam.

00:06:10.320 --> 00:06:14.160
Shia word has been derived from Sia

00:06:15.060 --> 00:06:19.420
The word which come from Sia became shia-Sia means Sitaji.

00:06:19.820 --> 00:06:24.220
If you go to UP (Uttar Pradesh, India) then nobody says Sitaji, they say Siaji,

00:06:24.860 --> 00:06:28.080
“Siavar Ramchandra Ki Jai”. Everyone takes the name Sia.

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:31.680
She was Sitaji, Adishakti herself

00:06:32.420 --> 00:06:36.800
and her two sons, who were Hassan and Hussain,

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:39.040
destroyed many evils.

00:06:39.820 --> 00:06:42.900
When they ultimately died after getting tried,

00:06:43.300 --> 00:06:48.740
then in the next birth they thought of establishment of non-violence, violence led them nowhere.

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:51.280
Experimenting

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:55.960
They were born as Mahavir and Buddha.

00:06:58.540 --> 00:07:00.540
Experiments do happen.

00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:05.940
After Nanak Sahab, around 50-60 years ago

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:08.920
in our Maharashtra Dattatreya incarnated

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:10.120
as Saibaba of Shirdi.

00:07:11.260 --> 00:07:15.140
If you want proof of it, then you get your realization

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:23.520
and after that if you put your hand on anyone,

00:07:23.620 --> 00:07:28.400
then you will get vibration of same kind-

00:07:28.620 --> 00:07:31.200
from just vibration only you can know about all.

00:07:31.420 --> 00:07:36.280
As you must have eyes to see any shape, its colour,

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:43.520
in the same way you are required to feel vibrations so that you may know all the Gurus of the world

00:07:43.700 --> 00:07:46.820
and will be able to know as who is a true Guru and who is a liar,

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:52.560
who is equal to that incarnation of Adiguru Dattatreya,

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:55.980
for mere saying there are thousands of Guru in modern times.

00:07:58.340 --> 00:08:03.740
No one become Guru just by saying of another.

00:08:03.980 --> 00:08:06.460
And by believing in him also, he does not become a Guru.

00:08:07.060 --> 00:08:11.500
The meaning of Guru Word is very large. This must be understood.

00:08:12.060 --> 00:08:15.020
Today I want to talk on this issue- who is a Guru and who is not.

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:18.280
The obvious meaning of Guru means the one who is bigger than us,

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:24.320
the one who is sitting at a place higher than us. As the water collected at a height spontaneously flows down,

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:32.100
it is also eager to find a surface for itself, and to bring everyone to its surface. You keep water to a certain height;

00:08:32.260 --> 00:08:34.440
it will be willing to (inaudible) everyone.

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:37.520
This is the very meaning of Guru.

00:08:37.820 --> 00:08:40.220
The one who is not that kind is not a Guru.

00:08:40.660 --> 00:08:45.340
He is above us in every matter, not just in one matter.

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:52.080
That is why we people who are wandering in street to street believing in Guru

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:57.140
should remember that the number of Gurus is in thousands.

00:08:57.320 --> 00:09:02.380
The Guru who talks of the absolute principle is a real Guru.

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:09.260
Those who talk of God and of God and who uplift you are real Gurus.

00:09:09.860 --> 00:09:13.220
Those who make money from you are not Gurus.

00:09:14.660 --> 00:09:18.720
Those who charge money for their speech, they can never be Gurus.

00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:22.540
Because the speech which has come from God is a precious thing,

00:09:23.260 --> 00:09:25.320
the value of which you just cannot give.

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:31.600
The day when you give value of it then that thing cannot be of God.

00:09:31.900 --> 00:09:34.840
You cannot go and purchase God from market.

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:37.740
Remember, today we are confronting

00:09:38.140 --> 00:09:43.160
thousands of such people who are making money in the name of God.

00:09:43.560 --> 00:09:47.500
Nothing can be bigger injustice and meanness than this.

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:54.000
If there is any article, substance or a thing in this world which is equal to the kick of the feet of the God,

00:09:54.640 --> 00:10:01.080
then we can say that we are watching God.

00:10:02.680 --> 00:10:06.760
You see, just now there was someone who came to our house, making himself to be greatest Guru,

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:13.440
started telling me that, ‘Shri Mataji you have all kind of things in your house, and you are working like a normal housewife,

00:10:14.080 --> 00:10:19.880
then how can you talk of God. I have given up this, I have given up that’.

00:10:20.980 --> 00:10:24.420
I told him that ‘if you genuinely know what is renouncing,

00:10:24.680 --> 00:10:28.020
then you should also know that, from all this things whatever you think is equal to dust of feet of my lord,

00:10:28.740 --> 00:10:36.320
is even equal to the particles, then you pick up that thing, but weigh equally.

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:39.620
He started watching here and there, saw this saw that.

00:10:39.620 --> 00:10:44.720
After that, he became embarrassed. I asked him, ‘did you discover anything?’

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:48.520
‘No, no. Nothing was found equal to what was asked for’.

00:10:48.520 --> 00:11:01.200
Then, I said, ‘son, what actually have you given up? What have you given up whose flag you are flowing from morning to evening, wearing saffron clothes and getting head bald, you are roaming in the whole world, crying.

00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:05.080
What have you given up? Only, this stones, this soil?’

00:11:08.980 --> 00:11:12.960
In reality sahaja yoga is getting nurtured in normal people who are leading a household life.

00:11:13.100 --> 00:11:19.040
Sahaja yoga can never nurture in those who dig their flags.

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:23.060
Those people who live with simple spontaneous emotions,

00:11:23.900 --> 00:11:26.900
who live in majesty given by God,

00:11:27.220 --> 00:11:31.340
in his happiness and joy, live with love,

00:11:33.260 --> 00:11:39.800
only such people of middle path reach to God.

00:11:42.900 --> 00:11:45.340
You should know what is the meaning of Guru

00:11:46.060 --> 00:11:50.860
Now those who collect money wearing saffron clothes, they can never be Gurus.

00:11:53.240 --> 00:12:01.520
Those who had once broken bicycles are now moving in Impala (car) can never be Gurus.

00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:06.360
The one who has found God, if he wishes he can sleep on the ground

00:12:06.820 --> 00:12:09.640
and if he wishes he can sleep in a palace comfortably.

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:12.580
For this reason I will give an example of King Janaka.

00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:19.620
Once a very great arch called Nachiketa went to the King Janaka. He was first suspicious and eager.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:22.680
He asked his Guru, ‘why do you pay visit to him since he is a householder

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:28.460
and also a king and then why do you bow down before him and touch his feet?

00:12:28.980 --> 00:12:33.500
He is a householder person!’Then he replied, ‘ok,

00:12:34.180 --> 00:12:38.140
you should go to the place of King Janaka and stay there.

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:42.980
You know that he is called as a videhi (beyond body), he was a dehati(a country person)’.

00:12:44.380 --> 00:12:50.000
When Nachiketa lived with him then he saw that there was so much wealth , people were eating and living comfortably.

00:12:50.140 --> 00:12:59.060
The King enjoyed all type of meals; he roams and has children –such a man, and how it is possible that this man should know God?

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:04.460
Next day he told that, “I am leaving just now, I’m just leaving now.

00:13:04.460 --> 00:13:06.380
I do not have to live here.’

00:13:06.500 --> 00:13:12.260
Then king said, ‘ok, let’s go for a bath first. They went to bath in a river. He took him to Sharayu River for bath.

00:13:13.900 --> 00:13:19.380
While bathing in a river, suddenly somebody informed that, ‘O Lord, your palace is on fire.’

00:13:19.500 --> 00:13:25.780
King Janaka said, ‘Let it be, just now I’m in meditation,’ he replied with a smile.

00:13:26.060 --> 00:13:29.240
This poor Nachiketa got little worried.

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:35.720
After a while people told that ‘all of your family member have to run away and fire is fast approaching you.’

00:13:35.860 --> 00:13:38.760
Then he said, ‘to hell with it, now I’m in meditation.’

00:13:39.160 --> 00:13:45.520
Afterwards they said that, ‘fire has reached up to here and all your ornaments and clothes will get burnt.’

00:13:45.900 --> 00:13:49.680
All the bodyguards also ran away.

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:55.440
This Nachiketa whose one or two clothes were lying outside – he thought that if these too were burnt then what will happen him

00:13:55.980 --> 00:14:02.240
So he also ran outside .He picked up all his clothes. Even then he (Janaka) was in meditation. When he came back,

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:05.640
Nachiketa was very much surprised. He asked ‘King, do you have not any worry that had your clothes been burnt

00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:07.000
then would you have moved just in this way.’ Then he replied,

00:14:07.060 --> 00:14:16.780
‘What is myth is going to be perished -there is no need to save it, till it is there keep it there or if it is not there then leave it.’

00:14:17.280 --> 00:14:28.860
This is a true fact. Those Gurus who do not consider myth as myth then what are you going to find in them.

00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:35.020
There is one occurrence in my in -laws family.

00:14:35.400 --> 00:14:38.680
Once there came a Barat (Wedding Procession) to our house.

00:14:39.840 --> 00:14:43.880
There was a demand of Dahi-Wada (a fried dish dipped in sweetened curd) from them.

00:14:44.080 --> 00:14:48.960
The Baratis usually have some coquetry and during the days of winter people told them,

00:14:49.280 --> 00:14:52.360
‘look in these days of winter it is very difficult to curdle because during winter evening curdling of milk is not done.’

00:14:52.460 --> 00:14:56.820
But they were adamant on having Dahi Wada -get it just now.

00:14:57.140 --> 00:15:01.960
In those times there used to live a baba (a wanderer).

00:15:01.980 --> 00:15:06.040
He was called for and was requested to arrange dish somehow.

00:15:06.260 --> 00:15:11.100
He replied that he would do it but then would not live here anymore.

00:15:11.920 --> 00:15:16.520
It was agreed and then he closed one window then another.

00:15:16.920 --> 00:15:24.420
After some time he said ‘look here it is your Dahi Wada now enjoy it.’ People began to eat dahi wadas- they were all happy.

00:15:24.660 --> 00:15:31.260
But Babaji ran away. He ran saving his life just in night. People could not understand why Babaji had to run away.

00:15:31.800 --> 00:15:40.740
Next day morning people from low caste came to take remaining of food.

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:43.140
They came and when they saw all the utensils,

00:15:43.940 --> 00:15:50.820
they began saying that who brought our pots here; these are our pots, who carried them here?

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:57.380
The marriage was accomplished somehow that is why the girl went to her in-laws house

00:15:57.640 --> 00:16:00.340
otherwise nobody could have sent her there.

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:02.440
The reason was that all the people had got annoyed.

00:16:02.640 --> 00:16:04.640
They started telling who brought the pots here?

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:06.180
Our ancestors and also those of my grandfather’s,

00:16:06.220 --> 00:16:10.780
did not believe in all these things, these were called Bhanamatis in Maharashtra,

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:19.880
nobody used to believe in all these things before, that something came from above(heaven) and they ate all the Dahi Wadas.

00:16:20.440 --> 00:16:25.760
You people should also think that does He have only one business to serve you people Dahi Wadas.

00:16:26.260 --> 00:16:30.080
When you make anybody a big Guru that he gives Rs.200 to you then I would say

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:36.800
if such are the donors then why not solve the economic problem? Give them all.

00:16:37.460 --> 00:16:41.200
They get you watches made in Switzerland.

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:43.880
We will believe only if they get one made by God.

00:16:44.140 --> 00:16:48.360
This must be considered that we want to get that supreme.

00:16:48.720 --> 00:16:51.960
But your seeking is also in these gross things,

00:16:51.960 --> 00:16:53.720
in these stones,

00:16:53.880 --> 00:16:55.880
money and wealth,

00:16:55.880 --> 00:16:57.180
that is why you consider these people as Gurus.

00:16:57.380 --> 00:17:02.740
Money is lost so is wealth. When all of your money is lost then you come to Me.

00:17:02.840 --> 00:17:04.840
Yesterday a woman came,

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:07.000
you saw her how she was dancing and jumping.

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:08.600
I asked her, ‘why have you come now?

00:17:08.820 --> 00:17:10.940
She replied, ‘what to do,

00:17:11.080 --> 00:17:15.540
I have become like this only!’ I said, ‘Ok, people make you fool and have I opened a mental hospital?

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:19.280
You went there to find what?’

00:17:19.580 --> 00:17:22.840
Can God be achieved by dancing and jumping?

00:17:25.160 --> 00:17:28.640
All the rules and regulations of our human beings,

00:17:28.860 --> 00:17:33.400
those people who made this laws had no idea that how disgust human beings can be?

00:17:33.860 --> 00:17:36.760
All those who have made these laws were very dignified

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:38.260
and very auspicious people.

00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:42.660
They could just not recognize the disgust

00:17:42.660 --> 00:17:45.740
and evilness that how much a human being is entangled in filthy jobs from within.

00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:48.540
If those people come to know then new laws have to be made

00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:50.420
to catch these people,

00:17:50.540 --> 00:17:52.120
all the people.

00:17:52.120 --> 00:17:53.700
Jesus Christ was crucified by these people.

00:17:53.700 --> 00:17:55.120
That was easy.

00:17:55.500 --> 00:18:02.900
But nobody can catch these people who are plundering money from you day and night

00:18:02.900 --> 00:18:04.960
and are bent on destroying you.

00:18:04.960 --> 00:18:08.140
