Up till now I have counted ten demons and six demoness who have come in this Kaliyuga.

00:33:37.680 --> 00:33:40.100
Nowadays, suppose Ravan comes here,

00:33:40.100 --> 00:33:42.360
then also he will never say that he is Ravan,

