if you see the eyes of cat then you will understand.

00:34:06.760 --> 00:34:08.180
Many people just don’t see many things.

00:34:08.180 --> 00:34:09.720
The eyes of cat- which has an eyeball inside- pupil of eye,

00:34:09.720 --> 00:34:11.900
as soon as you see it, it becomes small and in no time it disappears,

00:34:11.900 --> 00:34:14.420
it is just similar to the eyes of demons.

00:34:14.960 --> 00:34:16.960
I know them quite well.

00:34:17.100 --> 00:34:19.740
I have seen them in each and every birth.

00:34:19.940 --> 00:34:23.340
You can know them through their eyes that they are demons.

00:34:23.420 --> 00:34:25.800
Their pupil of eye just become small and disappears.

00:34:25.840 --> 00:34:27.840
This is their identification.

00:34:27.940 --> 00:34:30.020
Whether you can call them God or anything else,

00:34:30.160 --> 00:34:32.100
but they are demons.

00:34:32.100 --> 00:34:34.220
And these people have achieved many siddhis (achivements).

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:36.500
This is work of our bhole Shankarji, what to do?

00:34:36.500 --> 00:34:39.060
They (demons) have achieved many siddhis.

