00:35:09.260 --> 00:35:12.500
and kept on pouring darkness.

00:35:12.740 --> 00:35:14.740
Today in Kaliyuga, the situation is quite similar,

00:35:16.100 --> 00:35:20.240
and you are thinking that I have only two hands.

00:35:20.920 --> 00:35:24.980
It is your work and it will happen through you people only.

00:35:25.060 --> 00:35:28.580
You will be surprised because deities are also sitting at one side and demons on other.

