Today when I see this scene- what are these troubles?

00:35:33.660 --> 00:35:36.520
Is this because of your thinking?

00:35:36.980 --> 00:35:41.100
No, not at all! This devil and demons work through the pret yoni (dead spirits)

00:35:41.240 --> 00:35:44.100
and satiate you people so that you come running in their feet.

00:35:44.160 --> 00:35:46.160
All this is the work of these people.

00:35:48.600 --> 00:35:53.980
And if you have to defeat these people,

00:35:53.980 --> 00:35:56.280
then you have to lit the light in you.

00:35:56.280 --> 00:35:59.300
If you want to enlighten it, then all have to lit a light within themselves.

00:35:59.300 --> 00:36:01.660
You yourself will become a light.

00:36:02.020 --> 00:36:04.800
And what is surprising is-

00:36:05.000 --> 00:36:08.740
at this time God also wants that man should come on the stage,

00:36:08.740 --> 00:36:10.400
man himself should work.

00:36:10.580 --> 00:36:16.020
A man should become Parmatma Swaroop (form of God) and becomes a superman,

00:36:16.380 --> 00:36:18.760
there be establishment of superman.

00:36:18.900 --> 00:36:21.520
A new dimension is going to come in you.

00:36:21.620 --> 00:36:23.620
But the only thing is that you should learn to take it,

00:36:23.620 --> 00:36:25.120
should learn to absorb it.

00:36:25.300 --> 00:36:28.100
It cannot be compared with the standard of intelligence as of now,

00:36:28.100 --> 00:36:30.100
because if you try to understand through the intelligence,

00:36:30.160 --> 00:36:34.040
then you can only see my hand but not un-manifested streams

00:36:34.320 --> 00:36:36.320
which are flowing from them.

