Those people who are very big pandits,

00:36:41.200 --> 00:36:44.080
if they want they should read Kabir Das, Nanak ji

00:36:44.100 --> 00:36:47.420
and if possible also read Shankaracharya, he is the best.

00:36:47.500 --> 00:36:49.840
If you read Adi Shankaracharya then you can understand

00:36:49.920 --> 00:36:52.920
what is this Chaitanya Lahari (Vibrations), I am talking about.

