The same can be said about kundalini,

00:37:09.500 --> 00:37:12.300
I do not know on what basis.

00:37:12.540 --> 00:37:17.540
But still the witness state of human being is so high,

00:37:17.660 --> 00:37:19.660
so high that

00:37:19.660 --> 00:37:24.040
if you read Devi Bhagwat,

00:37:24.220 --> 00:37:26.500
Saptashati of Markendeya Swami then

00:37:26.520 --> 00:37:29.120
you will be surprised how deeply,

00:37:29.220 --> 00:37:33.320
in small detail they have understood this thing.

00:37:34.760 --> 00:37:38.740
The truth is unless and until you are realized anything you do is a waste.

00:37:38.880 --> 00:37:40.880
Krishna has said the same thing.

00:37:40.960 --> 00:37:44.120
Krishna has also said the same thing that first get him within.

00:37:44.660 --> 00:37:47.720
But those who were supposed to understand it could not understand it.

00:37:47.840 --> 00:37:50.560
He was saying to get him inside and you are saying go outside to fight.

00:37:50.560 --> 00:37:52.480
He meant that you should be a witness.

00:37:52.560 --> 00:37:55.060
It is happening in akarma (inaction) it is being done through you.

00:37:55.460 --> 00:38:00.540
You just do not do. Ego is finished and superego is finished.

00:38:00.540 --> 00:38:02.540
The one, who is a doer, is abolished.

00:38:02.560 --> 00:38:04.740
It was this, what he was talking about, but he was not listened to.

00:38:04.740 --> 00:38:06.580
He was a diplomat.

00:38:06.940 --> 00:38:09.460
Krishna has his own Guru tattwa.

00:38:09.600 --> 00:38:12.240
His Guru tattwa is also very interesting. He was a very big politician.

00:38:12.440 --> 00:38:16.220
I used to call him an absolute, pure politician.

00:38:16.820 --> 00:38:21.920
He was such a big politician, and he knew that this is the only way to get these fools alright.

00:38:23.600 --> 00:38:28.380
When a child tries to drive a cart by attaching his horses at back

00:38:28.620 --> 00:38:33.220
then his father comes and says, ‘keep whipping it, carry on, you will reach.’

00:38:33.700 --> 00:38:38.500
But after getting tired when a child thinks that the horse is just not moving,

00:38:38.540 --> 00:38:41.420
then he comes to know that first put the horse in front of the cart then whip it.

00:38:41.460 --> 00:38:43.680
Therefore he said to do karma yoga (yoga of action).

00:38:43.800 --> 00:38:46.540
Now here you should notice the diplomacy of Krishna.

00:38:47.280 --> 00:38:49.640
It is difficult to find a Guru like Krishna.

00:38:50.340 --> 00:38:54.740
He is such a Guru that requires a lot of intensity and depth of intelligence.

00:38:55.020 --> 00:38:58.780
What I am going to tell you now, no one would have told you this so far, you listen to it.

00:38:58.780 --> 00:39:00.780
He said that you do the action

00:39:00.880 --> 00:39:03.600
and leave the fruitfulness of action to God.

00:39:03.600 --> 00:39:06.780
It is just not possible, an absolute absurd condition.

00:39:06.980 --> 00:39:11.660
When you are doing something and you know it, then how can you leave it to someone else?

00:39:14.080 --> 00:39:16.440
You are keeping horse at back and whipping it.

00:39:16.620 --> 00:39:20.220
Secondly, he said that, ‘you do bhakti (devotion)’.

00:39:20.220 --> 00:39:22.720
See in it, it is very beautiful. You do the Ananya bhakti (absolute devotion),

00:39:22.880 --> 00:39:26.120
when there is no one else then how there can be devotion?

00:39:28.360 --> 00:39:31.400
Means that when union has taken place then whom to devote?

00:39:33.380 --> 00:39:36.500
He said, ‘Pushpam, Falam, Toyam’, whatever fruits, flowers, water you offer

00:39:36.500 --> 00:39:37.920
I will accept it.

00:39:37.920 --> 00:39:41.400
